<section id="section2">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2 class="colour2">What can JCSRS offer your family?</h2>
            <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="wrapper bg-colour2">
        <div class="container">
            <ul>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/b601fe647b4c173d6b45c88ad3c515ca.png" alt="SIS offers icon-6" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">ESF Network</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>As part of the English Schools Foundation(ESF), our students are supported by the largest English-medium international school organisation in Hong Kong, providing them the resources and opportunities not found outside of ESF Schools.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://jcsrs.esf.edu.hk/en/about_us/ESF_family/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/badff46189543e990172851e10209445.png" alt="Comprehensive Student Support" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Focus on Belonging</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>We prioritise student happiness, independence, and engagement, fostering a safe, welcoming environment that values belonging, dignity, and respect.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://jcsrs.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/wellbeing/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/d420ab852a6ae1f1da53caf6dd1dc1ec.png" alt="Well-equipped Facilities" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Inclusive Environment</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>We enable inclusive learning environments with high-quality learning experiences and outcomes.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://jcsrs.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/engagement/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/5d8eb14d8f9ff419cf7647e2ea2ef35c.png" alt="World-class Education" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Personalised Learning</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>We provide an adaptive curriculum tailored to meet the unique needs of each student and supported by therapeutic interventions.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://jcsrs.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/curriculum">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/9f7f2cd55cf04cb8b0ef788df5e326d7.png" alt="Strong School-Family Connection" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Collaborative Partnerships</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>We encourage learning partnerships between staff, families, and the wider community for holistic growth.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://jcsrs.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_people/parent_engagement/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/01bf5cc2bac133763a6c1687442e11e0.png" alt="Well-rounded Education" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Student Agency</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>Learning is designed to be engaging and responsive to individual needs where success and independence are recognised in multiple ways.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://jcsrs.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/activities_and_events/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(window).load(function() {
            $('h3', '#section2').each(function() {
                let img = $(this).parent().children('img');
                if(img.length) {
                    $(this).css('top', img.offset().top + img.height() + 25 - $(this).parent().offset().top);
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</section>
<section id="section3">
    <img src="/cache/img/c42cde15c7342718416749f9f93463ae.jpg" alt="learning" loading="lazy" width="1722" height="1294" />    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="section-title-container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2 class="colour2">Learning</h2>
                <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tabs">
                            <button class="tab current" data-id="1">Curriculum Pathways</button>
                            <button class="tab" data-id="2">Vocational Learning</button>
                            <button class="tab" data-id="3">Therapy Support</button>
                    </div>
        <select class="tab-select" name="tab"><option value="1">Curriculum Pathways</option><option value="2">Vocational Learning</option><option value="3">Therapy Support</option></select>                    <div class="tab-content current" data-id="1">
                                <article class="editor"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Our curriculum is personalised, progressive, and focused on global competencies.</span></p></article>
                                    <a href="https://jcsrs.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/curriculum/">
                        <span>Find out more</span>
                    </a>
                            </div>
                    <div class="tab-content" data-id="2">
                                <article class="editor"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">JCSRS offers vocational learning opportunities in the secondary curriculum, focusing on independent living, communication, job skills, and career planning. Students also benefit from job coaching support.</span></p></article>
                                    <a href="https://jcsrs.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/curriculum/">
                        <span>Find out more</span>
                    </a>
                            </div>
                    <div class="tab-content" data-id="3">
                                <article class="editor"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The therapy team at JCSRS collaborates with teachers and support staff to empower students, providing direct and indirect services to address various areas of development.&nbsp;</span></p></article>
                                    <a href="https://jcsrs.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/curriculum/">
                        <span>Find out more</span>
                    </a>
                            </div>
                <script type="text/javascript">
            $(document).ready(function() {
                $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section3').index() + 1) + ')', '#section3').hide();

                $('.tab', '#section3').click(function() {
                    $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section3').removeClass('current');
                    $(this).addClass('current');
                    $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).data('id') + ']', '#section3').addClass('current');
                    $('select', '#section3').val($(this).data('id')).selectbox('refresh');
                    $('.select .select-container div', '#section3').show();
                    $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section3').index() + 1) + ')', '#section3').hide();
                });

                $('.tab-select', '#section3').change(function() {
                    $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section3').removeClass('current');
                    $('.tab[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']').addClass('current');
                    $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']', '#section3').addClass('current');
                    $('.select .select-container div', '#section3').show();
                    $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section3').index() + 1) + ')', '#section3').hide();
                });
            });
        </script>
    </div>
</section>
