    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function() {
            $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section6').index() + 1) + ')', '#section6').hide();
            
            $('.tab', '#section6').click(function() {
                $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section6').removeClass('current');
                $(this).addClass('current');
                $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).data('id') + ']', '#section6').addClass('current');
                $('.tab-select .select-container div', '#section6').removeClass('current');
                $('.tab-select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($(this).index() + 1) + ')', '#section6').addClass('current');
                chkContentHeight();
            });

            $('.tab-select', '#section6').change(function() {
                $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section6').removeClass('current');
                $('.tab[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']', '#section6').addClass('current');
                $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']', '#section6').addClass('current');
                $('.tab-select .select-container div', '#section6').removeClass('current');
                $('.tab-select .select-container div:nth-child(' +  ($('.tab.current', '#section6').index() + 1) + ')', '#section6').addClass('current');
                $('.select .select-container div', '#section6').show();
                $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section6').index() + 1) + ')', '#section6').hide();
                chkContentHeight();
            });

            $('.record-slider', '#section6').Slider({
                slides: '.record-item',
                maxSlide: 1,
                swipeControl: true,
                skipBoundary: true,
                infiniteLoop: true
            });

            function chkContentHeight() {
                $('p.description', '#section6').each(function() {
                    if($(this).height() > 160) {
                        $(this).parent().addClass('more');
                    }
                });
            }
            chkContentHeight();

            $('.record-item article button.view-more', '#section6').click(function() {
                $(this).hide();
                $(this).parent().find('.view-less').show();
                $(this).parent().find('.description').hide();
                $(this).parent().find('.content').show();
            });
            $('.record-item article button.view-less', '#section6').click(function() {
                $(this).hide();
                $(this).parent().find('.view-more').show();
                $(this).parent().find('.description').show();
                $(this).parent().find('.content').hide();
            });
        });
    </script>
</section>
<section id="section7" data-total="10">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2 class="colour2">What's New at JCSRS?</h2>
            <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="record-slider">
        <div class="slider-container">
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="131">
                        <time>13/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>JCSRS are galloping into the Year of the Horse with a wide variety of engaging experiences and performances. We wish everyone a wonderful, prosperous and healthy year ahead! 🐎</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/9a584312f083a0c881b3a1f0f4a8a6cf.jpg" alt="634703946_1275551321333457_4845561035255667088_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="130">
                        <time>02/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>Our 40th Anniversary Fun Day was not only a celebration, but also a wonderful opportunity to connect with incredible organisations and partners that support neurodivergent students and adults in our Hong Kong community.<br><br>We were proud to have representatives from inspiring NGOs such as Youth Empowerment Service, The Nesbitt Centre, Sensational Foundation, ICHK Secondary and r é n, who shared information about their programmes and social enterprise products for sale.<br><br>A special thank you also to our corporate partner Manulife Hong Kong and Macau, whose team volunteered on the day and, just as importantly, provides vocational placements and meaningful work opportunities for neurodivergent young people.<br><br>It was especially meaningful to welcome back our alumni, who are now thriving in roles within these very NGOs: a beautiful illustration of our school's ethos extending beyond our walls and into the wider community.<br><br>It's through partnerships like these that we continue to build a more inclusive, supportive, and opportunity-rich community for all. Thank you for raising awareness and for being part of this important journey.<br><br>#JCSRS40 #FunDay #CommunityPartnerships</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/d37b9896931529c63850f62503a3ce58.jpg" alt="625465546_1265914278963828_2627708258274084899_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="129">
                        <time>29/01/2026</time>
                        <h3>Celebrating All Our Children at the JCSRS 40th Birthday Fun Day!<br><br>The JCSRS 40th Fun Day was a celebration dedicated to every child who makes our JCSRS community unique – this includes our students, their siblings, friends, and the children of our staff and colleagues. The Fun Day was designed specifically for them: a day to recognise their achievements, friendships, and kindness, and, above all, to have fun.<br><br>It was wonderful to see so many children take to the stage to share their talents. From seasoned performers to those playing for the very first time, we were treated to beautiful music by the JCSRS Orchestra, including moving renditions of "Ode to Joy" and "You Raise Me Up", and a vibrant Lunar New Year dance that filled the day with energy.<br><br>Most importantly, we want to say a heartfelt thank you to all the children who brought the day to life with your laughter, your play, and your wonderful spirit. You made the celebration unforgettable!<br><br>#JCSRS40 #CelebratingChildren</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/5b38f91e64d634e51e17e92979c73e8b.jpg" alt="623365922_1262606912627898_5722452884044468047_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="128">
                        <time>27/01/2026</time>
                        <h3>What a fantastic way to celebrate 40 years of JCSRS!<br><br>Seeing our whole community – students, families, staff, alumni, and partners – come together for a day of fun and connection was truly special. The atmosphere was full of laughter and positive energy, and it was wonderful to see everyone, especially all the children, enjoying the games, performances, and time with friends.<br><br>This event was a joyful reflection of our diverse and supportive community, and a fitting celebration of our school's 40-year journey. A sincere thank you to everyone who helped make it happen.<br><br>#JCSRS40 #FunDay #ESFCommunity #JCSRSCommunity</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/7d345148317fd33baba3ec3e7ef96aa6.jpg" alt="623352392_1260731092815480_576258300374341687_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="127">
                        <time>23/01/2026</time>
                        <h3>The wait is almost over – just one day to go!<br><br>Come celebrate 40 incredible years of JCSRS with our whole community tomorrow. Enjoy student performances, carnival games, delicious treats, and a magic show.<br><br>Let's make wonderful memories together.<br><br>#JCSRS40 #ESFCommunity</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/b8b4ec0642a0610b071057ee82ae4bc2.jpg" alt="621445084_1257263229828933_7455292633842640113_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="126">
                        <time>13/01/2026</time>
                        <h3>Join us in celebrating 40 incredible years of JCSRS!<br><br>#JCSRS40</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/0e3d119bd71abfad15388174ae9dae2d.jpg" alt="615422633_1249311080624148_1630181034398060900_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="125">
                        <time>12/01/2026</time>
                        <h3>You’re invited to our JCSRS 40th Anniversary Fun Day! 🎉<br><br>We are thrilled to extend an invitation to our friends, neighbours, and partners to celebrate a very special milestone – our 40th Anniversary!<br><br>Join us for a fantastic community day filled with fun, games, food, and memories. Our amazing PTA has been working hard to make this a day to remember.<br><br>📅 Date: Saturday, 24 January<br>⏰ Time: 10 am – 2 pm<br>📍 Location: JCSRS Campus<br><br>This is a wonderful opportunity to connect, celebrate, and experience the vibrant spirit of our school community. All are welcome: friends from other ESF schools, community partners, and supporters of JCSRS.<br><br>We look forward to celebrating this joyous occasion with you!<br><br>#JCSRS40 #ESFCommunity</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/1017617abd6a94b4a8c061d7ea5d9a9e.jpg" alt="615218078_1248754344013155_5913687169272373948_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="124">
                        <time>02/12/2025</time>
                        <h3>We Stand With Tai Po – ESF Fundraising Day this Friday, 5 December<br><br>You can donate using the FPS QR code in this post.</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/ba5bd349cd9ad06c2cc0dfae5272c291.jpg" alt="592867683_1218232713731985_4394947199095054958_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="123">
                        <time>26/11/2025</time>
                        <h3>Students in the Life Skills 1 and Life Skills 2 classes put their vocational learning into action with a hands-on manufacturing project, and the results are fantastic!<br><br>Working together through four key roles: material organiser, assembler, quality control, and packaging, they produced 140 beautiful keychains to be gifted at the JCSRS 40th Anniversary Performance. Congratulations to the students for their teamwork, focus and determination in making this project a success!<br><br>#VocationalLearning #JCSRS40</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/7b8939c64941256bd08ed3f19518d38c.jpg" alt="590076380_1213776274177629_665532005051079517_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="122">
                        <time>25/11/2025</time>
                        <h3>✨ The countdown is ON! ✨<br><br>Our 40th Anniversary celebrations are just around the corner, and JCSRS is buzzing with excitement!<br><br>We’ve been digging through the archives and are so excited to share a journey through time. From our humble beginnings with just seven students in 1985 to the vibrant community we are today, we can't wait to celebrate with you.<br><br>Get ready for:<br><br>🎭 A Magical Tour Through Time – our students have been working tirelessly on a spectacular performance that travels through the decades!<br><br>🛍️ 40th Anniversary merchandise – beautiful memorabilia, designed and created by our students, will be available for purchase.<br><br>👋 Alumni visits – we're so excited to welcome back our former students and hear their stories.<br><br>🎪 40th Anniversary Fun Day (24 January) – our amazing PTA is already preparing a fantastic community day for everyone!<br><br>Stay tuned for more updates. It’s going to be magical!<br><br>#JCSRS40 #ESF</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/a55042b00a4b498564f953ab1cf439dc.jpg" alt="561804410_1212914257597164_839536987217780463_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="131">
                        <time>13/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>JCSRS are galloping into the Year of the Horse with a wide variety of engaging experiences and performances. We wish everyone a wonderful, prosperous and healthy year ahead! 🐎</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/9a584312f083a0c881b3a1f0f4a8a6cf.jpg" alt="634703946_1275551321333457_4845561035255667088_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="130">
                        <time>02/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>Our 40th Anniversary Fun Day was not only a celebration, but also a wonderful opportunity to connect with incredible organisations and partners that support neurodivergent students and adults in our Hong Kong community.<br><br>We were proud to have representatives from inspiring NGOs such as Youth Empowerment Service, The Nesbitt Centre, Sensational Foundation, ICHK Secondary and r é n, who shared information about their programmes and social enterprise products for sale.<br><br>A special thank you also to our corporate partner Manulife Hong Kong and Macau, whose team volunteered on the day and, just as importantly, provides vocational placements and meaningful work opportunities for neurodivergent young people.<br><br>It was especially meaningful to welcome back our alumni, who are now thriving in roles within these very NGOs: a beautiful illustration of our school's ethos extending beyond our walls and into the wider community.<br><br>It's through partnerships like these that we continue to build a more inclusive, supportive, and opportunity-rich community for all. Thank you for raising awareness and for being part of this important journey.<br><br>#JCSRS40 #FunDay #CommunityPartnerships</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/d37b9896931529c63850f62503a3ce58.jpg" alt="625465546_1265914278963828_2627708258274084899_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="129">
                        <time>29/01/2026</time>
                        <h3>Celebrating All Our Children at the JCSRS 40th Birthday Fun Day!<br><br>The JCSRS 40th Fun Day was a celebration dedicated to every child who makes our JCSRS community unique – this includes our students, their siblings, friends, and the children of our staff and colleagues. The Fun Day was designed specifically for them: a day to recognise their achievements, friendships, and kindness, and, above all, to have fun.<br><br>It was wonderful to see so many children take to the stage to share their talents. From seasoned performers to those playing for the very first time, we were treated to beautiful music by the JCSRS Orchestra, including moving renditions of "Ode to Joy" and "You Raise Me Up", and a vibrant Lunar New Year dance that filled the day with energy.<br><br>Most importantly, we want to say a heartfelt thank you to all the children who brought the day to life with your laughter, your play, and your wonderful spirit. You made the celebration unforgettable!<br><br>#JCSRS40 #CelebratingChildren</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/5b38f91e64d634e51e17e92979c73e8b.jpg" alt="623365922_1262606912627898_5722452884044468047_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="128">
                        <time>27/01/2026</time>
                        <h3>What a fantastic way to celebrate 40 years of JCSRS!<br><br>Seeing our whole community – students, families, staff, alumni, and partners – come together for a day of fun and connection was truly special. The atmosphere was full of laughter and positive energy, and it was wonderful to see everyone, especially all the children, enjoying the games, performances, and time with friends.<br><br>This event was a joyful reflection of our diverse and supportive community, and a fitting celebration of our school's 40-year journey. A sincere thank you to everyone who helped make it happen.<br><br>#JCSRS40 #FunDay #ESFCommunity #JCSRSCommunity</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/7d345148317fd33baba3ec3e7ef96aa6.jpg" alt="623352392_1260731092815480_576258300374341687_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="127">
                        <time>23/01/2026</time>
                        <h3>The wait is almost over – just one day to go!<br><br>Come celebrate 40 incredible years of JCSRS with our whole community tomorrow. Enjoy student performances, carnival games, delicious treats, and a magic show.<br><br>Let's make wonderful memories together.<br><br>#JCSRS40 #ESFCommunity</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/b8b4ec0642a0610b071057ee82ae4bc2.jpg" alt="621445084_1257263229828933_7455292633842640113_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="126">
                        <time>13/01/2026</time>
                        <h3>Join us in celebrating 40 incredible years of JCSRS!<br><br>#JCSRS40</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/0e3d119bd71abfad15388174ae9dae2d.jpg" alt="615422633_1249311080624148_1630181034398060900_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="125">
                        <time>12/01/2026</time>
                        <h3>You’re invited to our JCSRS 40th Anniversary Fun Day! 🎉<br><br>We are thrilled to extend an invitation to our friends, neighbours, and partners to celebrate a very special milestone – our 40th Anniversary!<br><br>Join us for a fantastic community day filled with fun, games, food, and memories. Our amazing PTA has been working hard to make this a day to remember.<br><br>📅 Date: Saturday, 24 January<br>⏰ Time: 10 am – 2 pm<br>📍 Location: JCSRS Campus<br><br>This is a wonderful opportunity to connect, celebrate, and experience the vibrant spirit of our school community. All are welcome: friends from other ESF schools, community partners, and supporters of JCSRS.<br><br>We look forward to celebrating this joyous occasion with you!<br><br>#JCSRS40 #ESFCommunity</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/1017617abd6a94b4a8c061d7ea5d9a9e.jpg" alt="615218078_1248754344013155_5913687169272373948_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
